  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the raclette grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Season the cod fillets with salt, black pepper, and paprika.",
    "Brush the grill with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the cod fillets for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "While the fish is cooking, mix the lemon juice and garlic in a small bowl.",
    "Once the fish is done, brush the lemon juice mixture on top of each fillet.",
    "Serve the grilled fish with chilled butter and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Place the fish on the raclette grill and let each guest cook their own meal.",
    "Encourage guests to melt the chilled butter on top of the fish as they cook."
  ],
